     Best Western Le Galice Aix Centre-Ville, Aix-en-provence

Best Western Hotel Le Galice Aix Centre-Ville, Aix-en-provence

   5 Route De Galice, 13090, Aix-en-provence, France - See on a map
   Best Western Le Galice Aix Centre-Ville - Outdoor Swimming Pool The
   Best Western Le Galice Aix Centre-Ville is ideally located in the
   center of Aix-en-provence. Come and experience our hotel near the major
   tourist attractions. Best price guaranteed and exclusive deals.
   +33 4 42527527 Hotel website
   4.0/5 trip adv based on 715 traveler reviews

