"Business Visit - Handy for walking to centre of Aix"

   [blank.png] 3
   McLaddie, Cheshire, United Kingdom
   15/03/2018

   Stayed here for a couple of nights while on business. The room was
   fine, bed comfortable and everything clean. The restaurant staff were
   friendly and helpful, although it has to be said the food was fairly
   ordinary and dull. Breakfast was good. Handy free parking outside the
   hotel after 7pm and provided you left by 8am. Also hotel was easy to
   find with straightforward access off the motorway. Would stay again.

