"good value"

   [blank.png] 4
   gsabajr, New Orleans, La
   13/09/2015

   We stayed on Best Western Points and therefore felt that the value was
   very good. The breakfast was adequate. One morning we asked for fried
   eggs rather than the scrambled on the buffet and received delicious
   ones, but the next morning we were told that there was not a cook
   available. The rooms were clean and the people at the reception desk
   very helpful. The wireless internet in our room was annoying in that
   the logon and password were very complex and we were required to put it
   all in each time we logged on which was frequent as we kept getting
   kicked off. It worked well while we were on. Bed was comfortable and
   the shower and bathroom excellent..

"Much better than our expectation. Bravo!"

   [blank.png] 5
   Kassavetis, Tripoli, Greece
   12/09/2015

   Hotel le Galice was a nice surprise for us. Great value for money. Good
   location, about 5 minutes walk away from the city center. Nice, clean
